highlights.text: MXZI has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “MONTAGEM TOMADA” is the highest at #16.
“Tinh Iu Mau Nang” by Duong Van Tuyen is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #61.
“Cry For Me” by Michita and 愛海 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 127 days straight.
“MONTAGEM TOMADA - Super Slowed” by MXZI is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 16 spots at #78.
